description:
Dear MonetDB Developers,

I encountered an unexpected execution result. If you have the opportunity to take a look, I would greatly appreciate your time and efforts. Let's make MonetDB more robust!

```sql
CREATE TABLE t0(c0 INT, c1 INT);

INSERT INTO t0(c0, c1) VALUES(-2, 1);

SELECT * FROM t0 WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM (VALUES (t0.c1)) WHERE (NOT (r'' NOT ILIKE r'')) AND FALSE);
-- Wrong Execution Result: Empty Result
-- Expected Result: -2, 1

```
